@startuml deployment-authority-boundary
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title Deployment Context and Authority Boundaries (Web-First Multiplayer)

node "Browser Client A\n(Host authority)" as Host {
  component "Game Scenes\n(UI + Card logic)" as HostUI
  component "MultiplayerCardManager" as HostMCM
  component "ConnectionManager" as HostConn
  component "GDSync + LocalServerSignaling" as HostSync
}

node "Browser Client B\n(Peer)" as Peer1 {
  component "Game Scenes\n(UI + Card logic)" as PeerUI
  component "MultiplayerCardManager" as PeerMCM
  component "ConnectionManager" as PeerConn
  component "GDSync + LocalServerSignaling" as PeerSync
}

node "Browser Client C\n(Peer)" as Peer2 {
  component "Game Scenes\n(UI + Card logic)" as Peer2UI
  component "MultiplayerCardManager" as Peer2MCM
  component "ConnectionManager" as Peer2Conn
  component "GDSync + LocalServerSignaling" as Peer2Sync
}

cloud "Signaling/Relay Server\n(Python HTTP/SSE)" as Relay

HostSync --> Relay : HTTP actions\n(connect/create/join/broadcast)
PeerSync --> Relay : HTTP actions
Peer2Sync --> Relay : HTTP actions

Relay --> HostSync : SSE events
Relay --> PeerSync : SSE events
Relay --> Peer2Sync : SSE events

HostMCM -[#green,bold]-> HostMCM : authoritative validation\nand canonical updates
PeerMCM -[#gray,dashed]-> HostMCM : proposes move intent\n(via relay path)
Peer2MCM -[#gray,dashed]-> HostMCM : proposes move intent\n(via relay path)

rectangle "In-process boundary\n(signals/local callbacks)" as InProc #E6F4EA
rectangle "Inter-client boundary\n(HTTP/SSE relay)" as InterNet #FFF4E6

InProc .. HostConn
InProc .. HostMCM
InProc .. PeerConn
InProc .. PeerMCM
InProc .. Peer2Conn
InProc .. Peer2MCM

InterNet .. Relay

legend right
|= Boundary |= Meaning |
| Host authority | Final move validation and state convergence |
| In-process signals | Local component communication inside one client |
| HTTP/SSE relay | Cross-client event propagation for web deployment |
endlegend

@enduml

